 style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">{your</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}},</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">{your</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> requested</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> ppm</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}},</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">\\t\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}</span></span></code></pre><p>The key components of this message are:</p><ul>\\n<li><code>address</code> - The address of the order router that will receive the revenue share. This is also the id you place in your order message</li>\\n<li><code>sharePpm</code> - The revenue share percentage in parts per million (ppm).</li>\\n</ul><p>After submitting the proposal, it must go through the standard governance voting process and receive a passing vote before the order router address and revenue share percentage are activated in the system.</p></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/integration/integration-revshare.mdx#voting-in-via-governance\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"To participate in the Order Router Rev Share program, you need to create and submit a governance proposal. Below is an example of what the governance message structure looks like:message Order {\\n&quot;messages&quot;: [\\n\\t{\\n\\t\\t&quot;@type&quot;: &quot;/dydxprotocol.revshare.MsgSetOrderRouterRevShare&quot;,\\n\\t\\t&quot;authority&quot;: authority,\\n\\t\\t&quot;order_router_rev_share&quot;: {\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;address&quot;: {{your address}},\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;: {{your requested ppm}},\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n]\\n}The key components of this message are:\\naddress - The address of the order router that will receive the revenue share. This is also the id you place in your order message\\nsharePpm - The revenue share percentage in parts per million (ppm).\\nAfter submitting the proposal, it must go through the standard governance voting process and receive a passing vote before the order router address and revenue share percentage are activated in the system.\",\"title\":\"Voting in via Governance\",\"titles\":[\"Revenue Share\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/integration/integration-revshare#updating-revenue-share-optional\",\"html\":\"<p>The process for updating an existing order router&#x27;s revenue share is the same as setting up a new one. You will need to submit a governance proposal with the updated parameters.</p><p>To update the revenue share percentage for an existing order router, create a governance message with the same structure:</p><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;messages&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: [</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">\\t{</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;@type&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;/dydxprotocol.revshare.MsgSetOrderRouterRevShare&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;authority&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">authority</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;order_router_rev_share&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t\\t&quot;address&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">{your</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> existing</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}},</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">{your</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> new</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> requested</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> ppm</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}},</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">\\t\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span></code></pre><p>The proposal must go through the standard governance voting process and receive a passing vote before the updated revenue share percentage takes effect.</p><aside data-callout=\\\"note\\\"><ul>\\n<li>You must use the exact same address that was previously approved</li>\\n<li>The update will completely replace the previous configuration once approved</li>\\n</ul></aside></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/integration/integration-revshare.mdx#updating-revenue-share-optional\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"The process for updating an existing order router&#x27;s revenue share is the same as setting up a new one. You will need to submit a governance proposal with the updated parameters.To update the revenue share percentage for an existing order router, create a governance message with the same structure:&quot;messages&quot;: [\\n\\t{\\n\\t\\t&quot;@type&quot;: &quot;/dydxprotocol.revshare.MsgSetOrderRouterRevShare&quot;,\\n\\t\\t&quot;authority&quot;: authority,\\n\\t\\t&quot;order_router_rev_share&quot;: {\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;address&quot;: {{your existing address}},\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;: {{your new requested ppm}},\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n]The proposal must go through the standard governance voting process and receive a passing vote before the updated revenue share percentage takes effect.\\nYou must use the exact same address that was previously approved\\nThe update will completely replace the previous configuration once approved\\n\",\"title\":\"Updating Revenue Share (Optional)\",\"titles\":[\"Revenue Share\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/integration/integration-revshare#deleting-an-order-router-rev-share-optional\",\"html\":\"<p>To delete an order router&#x27;s revenue share configuration, you simply need to set the revenue share percentage to 0. This process follows the same governance workflow as setting up or updating a revenue share.</p><p>Submit a governance proposal with the following message structure:</p><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;messages&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: [</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">\\t{</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;@type&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&quot;/dydxprotocol.revshare.MsgSetOrderRouterRevShare&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;authority&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">authority</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t&quot;order_router_rev_share&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t\\t&quot;address&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: {</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">{your</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> existing</span><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\"> address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}},</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#8DDB8C\\\">\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">: </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">0</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">\\t\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#B31D28;font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FF938A;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\\\">\\t}</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">]</span></span></code></pre><aside data-callout=\\\"note\\\"><p>Key points to note:</p><ul>\\n<li>Setting <code>sharePpm</code> to 0 effectively disables the revenue share for that order router</li>\\n<li>The address must match the previously approved order router address</li>\\n<li>The proposal must still pass through the standard governance voting process</li>\\n<li>Once approved, the order router will no longer receive any revenue share</li>\\n</ul><p>After the proposal passes, any orders that include this order router address will no longer generate revenue share for the router.</p></aside></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/integration/integration-revshare.mdx#deleting-an-order-router-rev-share-optional\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"To delete an order router&#x27;s revenue share configuration, you simply need to set the revenue share percentage to 0. This process follows the same governance workflow as setting up or updating a revenue share.Submit a governance proposal with the following message structure:&quot;messages&quot;: [\\n\\t{\\n\\t\\t&quot;@type&quot;: &quot;/dydxprotocol.revshare.MsgSetOrderRouterRevShare&quot;,\\n\\t\\t&quot;authority&quot;: authority,\\n\\t\\t&quot;order_router_rev_share&quot;: {\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;address&quot;: {{your existing address}},\\n\\t\\t\\t&quot;sharePpm&quot;: 0,\\n\\t\\t}\\n\\t}\\n]Key points to note:\\nSetting sharePpm to 0 effectively disables the revenue share for that order router\\nThe address must match the previously approved order router address\\nThe proposal must still pass through the standard governance voting process\\nOnce approved, the order router will no longer receive any revenue share\\nAfter the proposal passes, any orders that include this order router address will no longer generate revenue share for the router.\",\"title\":\"Deleting an Order Router Rev Share (Optional)\",\"titles\":[\"Revenue Share\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/integration/integration-revshare#changes-to-the-order-message\",\"html\":\"<p>The <code>order_router_address</code> field is set when an order is placed</p><ul>\\n<li><code>order_router_address</code> - the ID of the order router and where fees will be sent to</li>\\n</ul><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">message Order {</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">  // The unique ID of this order. Meant to be unique across all orders.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">  OrderId order_id </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">=</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 1</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> [ (gogoproto.nullable) </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">=</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> false</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> ];</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">  ...</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#6A737D;--shiki-dark:#768390\\\">  // order_router_address is the metadata for the frontend order router.</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">  string</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> order_router_address </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">=</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> 13</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">}</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-depth=\\\"2\\\">\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/integration/integration-revshare.mdx#changes-to-the-order-message\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"The order_router_address field is set when an order is placed\\norder_router_address - the ID of the order router and where fees will be sent to\\nmessage Order {\\n  // The unique ID of this order. Meant to be unique across all orders.\\n  OrderId order_id = 1 [ (gogoproto.nullable) = false ];\\n  ...\\n  // order_router_address is the metadata for the frontend order router.\\n  string order_router_address = 13;\\n}\",\"title\":\"Changes to the Order Message\",\"titles\":[\"Revenue Share\"]},{\"href\":\"/interaction/integration/integration-revshare#order-validation-checks\",\"html\":\"<ul>\\n<li>Ensure the <code>order_router_address</code> field is valid and already voted in via governance</li>\\n</ul></div></div>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/interaction/integration/integration-revshare.mdx#order-validation-checks\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nEnsure the order_router_address field is valid and already voted in via governance\\n\",\"title\":\"Order Validation Checks\",\"titles\":[\"Revenue Share\"]}]}}"
